<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-59-1055 </DOCNO><TEXT>The authors say it is time for a new nuclear policy for the Atlantic alliance.It should be that nuclear weapons will not be used unless an aggressoruses them first. This policy, with its accompaniment of a reduced requirementfor new Allied nuclear systems, should allow a considerable reductionin fears of all sorts. The authors say it will reduce the risk of conventionalaggression in Europe.</TEXT></DOC>